Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.43,0:02:09.39,OPCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HF4C1FA&\be0}将这无聊至极的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.39,0:02:12.52,OPCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HAB755B&}整个变成电影一般
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.52,0:02:15.48,OPCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HC2A6AF&}如此契机已经出现
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.48,0:02:18.61,OPCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HC9995A&}无法融入的晴空下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.61,0:02:21.53,OPCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HC9995A&}紧闭心扉落下心锁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.53,0:02:24.66,OPCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&H97C5D6&}如此一路艰难求生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.66,0:02:26.70,OPCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HC9995A&}旋律不断重叠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.70,0:02:33.46,OPCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&H97C5D6&}比街角的灯光再弱也无妨
